  <prompt>Wire callbacks from the overflow menu in NarrativeBullet up through ActivityNotesSection to DailyBriefingApp's existing handlers: Mark as read = R3 Check; Remove from briefing = R3 Remove; Keep on briefing for 7 more days = R3 Keep; Add to To Do = R2 useInlineTodoCreate per ADR-024; Dismiss + Open record are new. Reference handler pattern from `DailyBriefingApp.tsx` lines 238-287 (`handleAddToTodo`).</prompt>
  <role>SPAARKE platform developer. Follow ADRs strictly. Expert in Fluent UI v9 + React hooks + Xrm.WebApi.</role>
  <goal>All 6 overflow actions invoke the correct handler at DailyBriefingApp level. R3 actions (Check/Remove/Keep) behave identically to R3 (no regression). Add to To Do uses ADR-024 path unchanged. Dismiss + Open record are wired to new handlers.</goal>
