  <steps>
    <step order="1">Inspect DailyBriefingApp.tsx lines 238-287 (`handleAddToTodo`); inventory existing R3 handlers (Check/Remove/Keep) + their signatures</step>
    <step order="2">In DailyBriefingApp, add new handlers `handleDismiss` and `handleOpenRecord` (Open record stub delegates to NarrativeBullet's link handler from task 047 — for now, accept the call and log; task 047 supplies the navigation)</step>
    <step order="3">Add a single dispatch function `handleBulletAction(bulletId, actionId)` that switches on actionId and calls the right per-action handler</step>
    <step order="4">Pass `handleBulletAction` down through ActivityNotesSection prop to NarrativeBullet's `onAction`</step>
    <step order="5">Verify Add to To Do path still uses `useInlineTodoCreate` + `TODO_REGARDING_CATALOG` per ADR-024 (no regression)</step>
    <step order="6">Add Jest tests: each of 6 actions invokes the correct handler; useInlineTodoCreate is called for Add to To Do; handlers receive correct bulletId</step>
    <step order="7">Run `npm test`; ensure pass</step>
