  <notes>Sequential with task 045 (depends on its single-callback prop shape). HIGH OVERLAP RISK with R3 PR #451 (DailyBriefingApp.tsx + ActivityNotesSection.tsx + NarrativeBullet.tsx). Run conflict-check. Open record handler is intentionally minimal — task 047 supplies the Xrm.Navigation.navigateTo call. Justification: extension of existing R3 handlers (Check/Remove/Keep); 2 new handlers (Dismiss/Open record); cost-of-doing-nothing = no overflow menu functionality.</notes>
